{"tid":993031,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(有圖慎入）喉嚨同扁桃腺腫起一粒粒同生白色點點","createTime":"2019-01-23T15:06:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-28T14:29:56.000Z","uid":212514,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"588e9045bd2bc3c4baa81be5f978f31773418632","tid":993031,"uid":212514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T15:06:24.000Z","msg":"有啲核突<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n慎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n入<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Edh204T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEdh204T.png&h=b7699363&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dckDzpU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdckDzpU.png&h=3d348329&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日食完飯就feel到喉嚨有嘢銀住<br />\n好似有嘢痴住左喉嚨咁<br />\n跟住照下塊鏡就見到生左粒白色嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後夜晚再睇就變咗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有諗過係咪扁桃腺發炎 但係見人哋個個都好痛<br />\n我而家完全唔痛 淨係就feel到腫左<br />\n有冇ching 試過咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e1cf2618d43859e121d8ea76fd1c56ea916dd4b","tid":993031,"uid":137096,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T15:08:07.000Z","msg":"下世小心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a19f7321855ecc72c5c2d5fdf2fd6d3aafce4cd","tid":993031,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T15:09:08.000Z","msg":"近排有冇同人含過"},{"pid":"8a4f511cf16e9c1ee78993053c4e9283826b0cbc","tid":993031,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T15:09:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"050babc756118b52d7bbf163bd76f6094d68c0e6","tid":993031,"uid":838,"like